<h3>Status of defence industry</h3>
<ol>
<li>80k cr. industry with 80% public, 20% private participation</li>
<li>Despite being the third largest defence budget India is the second largest importer of arms (9.5% of world arms, after saudi (11%)) SIPRI</li>
<li>IMPORT DEPENDENCE = 65-70% defence equipments are imported.</li></ol>
